                {
                    "line_number": 1,
                    "line_text": "Le parc rit de rayons ramisés,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "3+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 2,
                    "line_text": "De baisers, d'éclats de voix de femmes…",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "3+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 3,
                    "line_text": "L'air sent bon, il est tout feux tout flammes",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "3+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 4,
                    "line_text": "Et les cœurs, aussi, vont embrasés.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "3+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Le parc rit de rayons ramisés,\nDe baisers, d'éclats de voix de femmes…\nL'air sent bon, il est tout feux tout flammes\nEt les cœurs, aussi, vont embrasés."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Une flûte au loin sonne la charge",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "3+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Des amours altières et frivoles,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "3+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Des amours sincères et des folles,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "3+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Et de l'Amour multiforme et large.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "9",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Une flûte au loin sonne la charge\nDes amours altières et frivoles,\nDes amours sincères et des folles,\nEt de l'Amour multiforme et large."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Décor charmant, peuple aimable et fier ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "9",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Tout n'est là que jeunesse et que joie,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "3+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "On perçoit des frôlements de soie,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "3+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "On entend des croisements de fer.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "3+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Décor charmant, peuple aimable et fier ;\nTout n'est là que jeunesse et que joie,\nOn perçoit des frôlements de soie,\nOn entend des croisements de fer."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Maintes guitares bourdonnent, guêpes",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "9",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Du désir élégant et farouche :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "3+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "— « Beau masque, on sait tes yeux et ta bouche. »",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+3",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Des mots lents flottent comme des crêpes.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "3+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Maintes guitares bourdonnent, guêpes\nDu désir élégant et farouche :\n— « Beau masque, on sait tes yeux et ta bouche. »\nDes mots lents flottent comme des crêpes."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "Pourtant, c'est trop beau, pour dire franc…",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "3+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Un pressentiment fait comme une ombre",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+3",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "À ce tableau d'extases sans nombre,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+3",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Et du noir rampe au nuage blanc !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "3+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Pourtant, c'est trop beau, pour dire franc…\nUn pressentiment fait comme une ombre\nÀ ce tableau d'extases sans nombre,\nEt du noir rampe au nuage blanc !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 6,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "Ô l'incroyable mélancolie",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "9",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "Tombant soudain sur la noble fête !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "9",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "De l'orage ? ô non, c'est la tempête !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "3+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "L'ennui, le souci ? — C'est la folie !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+3",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Ô l'incroyable mélancolie\nTombant soudain sur la noble fête !\nDe l'orage ? ô non, c'est la tempête !\nL'ennui, le souci ? — C'est la folie !"
        }
    ],
